---
title: Sticky Chili-Garlic Tofu and Green Beans with Crispy Shallot Rice
description: Get ready for everyone's favourite Canadian-Chinese takeout dish made at home! You won't have to sacrifice convenience for flavour, since tonight's recipe comes together in just a few simple steps. Tofu is cooked in a sweet and savoury sauce with crunch-tastic crispy shallots sprinkled over top!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tofu-collant-et-haricots-verts-aux-piments-et-a-lail-3efb3928.jpg
